{"tid":1492622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【突發】日本反送中第一人 模特兒平野鈴子小姐IG出事!","createTime":"2019-08-21T02:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T08:56:06.000Z","uid":13353,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6515ffa11ba6e8be538a0a7a92e4b650ce8ee5f6","tid":1492622,"uid":13353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:14:28.000Z","msg":"【突發】蘋果新聞 Translate 做英文譯咗做Beijing !!!<br />\n正當香港逆權運動登上國際舞台，中國除了發動國家機器在Facebook 及twitter 抺黑外，疑似在翻譯上出手。<br />\n在日本人平野玲子小姐 Suzuko Hirano 的ig 上發現，提及「蘋果新聞」，翻譯成英文時竟然出現「Beijing」！此舉大大扭曲玲子小姐原post 意思，隨時令不明所以的外國人誤會！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KLsn3B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KLsn3B&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41LccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=ac9524bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KLsn3B</a>"},{"pid":"f791587cfd447757a282f0c39cc626c72edac6ce","tid":1492622,"uid":13353,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"Suzuko Hirano<br />\n7小時 &middot; <br />\n&quot; Clarification 澄清宣言 申し開き書 &quot;<br />\n<br />\nIn the first place, and the upcoming future, I will keep my love to Hong Kong. It will never be changed. So please not to be deceived by the smear that amending Instagram translation of &quot;蘋果日報&quot; from &quot;Apple Daily&quot; to &quot;Beijing&quot;. I will fight with Hong Kong citizens till the end.<br />\n<br />\n一直以來我都深愛著香港，從今以後，都不會改變。請各位不要因為敵人的抹黑-蘋果日報翻譯成北京-所欺騙。我會和香港人一同戰鬥到最後一刻。<br />\n<br />\n私は今迄もこれからも香港を愛しその心が変わる事は一生ありません。敵の工作で蘋果日報が北京と翻訳されますが騙されないで下さい。私は最後まで香港人と一緒です。"},{"pid":"323f0524d060ff5f68d4b84712d8e61c17a5b797","tid":1492622,"uid":13353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69161640_1085471608509273_594597462891560960_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQlfwOur1UVRRX6Q7Y1qfvGnVLc3RCs0BW2YILdSWA0tKWAwUMdtrAwHX7gd2vombi8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=41606c6b92bcc62f0924ae287db28aa3&amp;oe=5E0D97B8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69161640_1085471608509273_594597462891560960_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQlfwOur1UVRRX6Q7Y1qfvGnVLc3RCs0BW2YILdSWA0tKWAwUMdtrAwHX7gd2vombi8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D41606c6b92bcc62f0924ae287db28aa3%26oe%3D5E0D97B8&h=88efba43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f16e023f227ee8d7a1fb527d0e6c5627562df621","tid":1492622,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:15:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1491552/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1491552/page/1</a><br />\n［ 8 2 4 和 你 suck ］行 動 更 新<br />\n建議大家不再分和理非勇武，合力&quot;搞&quot;好香港經濟先可以嬴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMbmerh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMbmerh.jpg&h=ba74c090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d0df31f9056836d4289609bfb3e82ff6ccb7b31","tid":1492622,"uid":13353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69304375_1085471641842603_3341873710389788672_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQkPr2emVMRMuk_PinJJcYX0d0pcRDdtY5IhYkcfIEKjzrx-Eh4f6-GJhjOpS-YkY3E&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=433466bf7581d60b9f587d0e6999734a&amp;oe=5DCC2BD0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69304375_1085471641842603_3341873710389788672_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQkPr2emVMRMuk_PinJJcYX0d0pcRDdtY5IhYkcfIEKjzrx-Eh4f6-GJhjOpS-YkY3E%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D433466bf7581d60b9f587d0e6999734a%26oe%3D5DCC2BD0&h=f6ef955a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"302889f49463e7922dbd0de33fdcc14ba5e4204a","tid":1492622,"uid":13353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"推到facebook 仆街"},{"pid":"3e8eee6042f7f33e94cc297ec90b63c350f35e30","tid":1492622,"uid